Fixed a problem with navigation from a Collection Index; Improved iCal Export to allow a non-contiguous selection; Improved File Open function to support either projects or collections; Added special class Values for use with outlining; Fixed an Outline tab bug; Improved the Tasks by Date sort; Added a new Starter Pack that uses the PARA organizing method. 

