Body:

##### Fixed Index Navigation

Fixed a problem with navigation from a page containing a [[Generate a Collection Index]] command.

##### Improved iCal Export

Made a change to the [[Context Menu]] Export to iCal function so that the selected notes need not be in a continuous range.

##### Modified File Open Functionality

When invoking the *File > Open* command, Notenik will now allow the user to select any folder or file, and will then do its best to open the specified (or enclosing) folder as either a [[project folder]] or a [[collection folder]], depending on the contents of the folder.

##### Added Special Class Values for Outlining

Added three [[Special Class Values]] to be used for outlining: `header`, `item` and `action`.

##### Fixed an Outline Tab Bug

There was a bug on the [[Outline Tab]] that sometimes erred in assigning children to parents. This has been corrected.

##### Tasks by Date Sort Improved

When sorting a Collection using *Tasks by Date* the [[Seq]] field is no longer included as a column in the table if the Collection is using the [[Outline Tab]] with the Seq field.

##### Added a New Starter Pack

Added a [[PARA Pack]] as another option when creating a new Collection. 
